quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  44,43,"Pellet, leggal Zaqquumi ngal"
  44,44,ko √Īaametee bakkondim…ďe …ďen
  44,45,A sikkay ko taayinaa ; hino fata ka nder deedi
  44,46,Wano wul…óam fatirta
  44,47,Nanngee mo poo…óiron ka hakkunde dul…ďaynge
  44,48,"refti yuppon ka hoore makko, lepte fatinaa…óe …óen"
  44,49,"Mee…óu non ! An [sikkunoo…óo] ko a foolu…óo, teddu…óo"
  44,50,Awa ko …óum woni kon ko sikkiti…óon e mum
  44,51,"Pellet, gom…óu…ďe …ďen wonii e weerde hoolniinde"
  44,52,e nder gese e …ďulli
  44,53,"hi…ďe …ďoornoo ko …óaati e ko tekki, hara hi…ďe fewtondiri"
  44,54,Ko wano non. Men resini …ďe kadi yaaju…ďe gite
  44,55,"Hi…ďe nodda toon, kala muuyantee…ói, hara ko …ďe hoolii…ďe"
  44,56,"∆Āe mee…óataa ton maayde, si wanaa maayde aranere nden. O da…ónda …ďe lepte Jahiimi …óen"
  44,57,"ko dokkal non, immorde ka Joomi maa. Awa ko …óum woni maloore mawnde nden"
  44,58,"Ko Men newiniri nde e …óamngal maa…óa, ko no …ďe waajitora"
  44,59,Habiito. Kam…ďe ko …ďe habbitii…ďe